# The bootstrap updater sidecar is built (by CI, or locally via
# `cargo build --release -p arcade_updater`) and staged here with a target-triple
# suffix before `tauri build` bundles it. The built binaries are not committed.
updater-*
# Stream-engine sidecar + its runtime DLLs are downloaded from the engine's public
# release and staged here by CI before `tauri build`. Never committed.
arcade-stream-engine*
*.dll
!.gitignore
